snippet.title: Destroy All Humans! – Clone Carnage – Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Tired of playing with yourself all alone? Good news: Clone Carnage, the stand-alone multiplayer mode for Destroy All Humans! is OUT NOW and free to play!*

Grab a friend for some hot split screen action on your couch or go online for an intense foursome. Dress up in all skins from Destroy All Humans! – if you’re into that.

*Free on PC and Xbox. The PlayStation version is available for 0.01 $ in the US / 0.25 € in the EU / 0.99 $ in SEA. 

- Links & Info -
Steam: https://thqn.net/dahcc-steam
PlayStation: https://thqn.net/dahcc-playstation
Xbox: https://thqn.net/dahcc-xbox
Website: https://www.destroyallhumansgame.com
Discord: https://discord.gg/destroy
